### Flujo de Registro de Envío (Operario → Tiempo Real)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant OP as Operario (Frontend)
    participant AUTH as Spring Security
    participant API as EnvioController
    participant DB as MySQL
    participant SCHED as Scheduler (cada Ta seg)
    participant ACS as ACSAdapter
    participant WS as WebSocket
    participant AER as Aerolínea (Frontend)

    OP->>AUTH: POST /api/auth/login {user, pass}
    AUTH-->>OP: JWT {rol: OPERARIO}

    OP->>API: POST /api/envios {origen, destino, maletas, aerolineaId}
    Note over API: Header: Authorization: Bearer JWT
    AUTH->>AUTH: Verificar rol = OPERARIO o ADMIN
    API->>DB: INSERT envio (estado=PENDIENTE, simulacion_id=NULL, operario_id=X)
    API-->>OP: 201 Created {envioId}

    Note over SCHED: Cada Ta segundos
    SCHED->>DB: SELECT envios WHERE simulacion_id IS NULL AND estado=PENDIENTE ORDER BY fecha_hora_registro LIMIT Sc
    SCHED->>ACS: planificar(subInput, Ta*1000)
    ACS-->>SCHED: Resultado
    SCHED->>DB: UPDATE envio SET estado=EN_RUTA/ENTREGADO
    SCHED->>DB: INSERT asignacion_envio (tramos de ruta)
    SCHED->>WS: SEND /topic/tiempo-real {métricas globales}
    SCHED->>WS: SEND /topic/mis-envios/{aerolineaId} {envíos actualizados}
    WS-->>AER: "Su envío ENV-001 está EN_RUTA: SPJC → KMIA → LEMD"
```

### Flujo de Simulación (Admin)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant AD as Admin (Frontend)
    participant AUTH as Spring Security
    participant SC as SimulationController
    participant SS as SimulationService
    participant DB as MySQL
    participant ACS as ACSAdapter
    participant WS as WebSocket

    AD->>AUTH: POST /api/auth/login {user, pass}
    AUTH-->>AD: JWT {rol: ADMIN}

    AD->>SC: POST /api/simulacion/iniciar {Sa, K, Ta, fechaInicio, fechaFin}
    AUTH->>AUTH: Verificar rol = ADMIN
    SC->>SS: iniciarSimulacion(config)
    SS->>DB: Verificar cobertura de datos en rango
    alt No hay datos suficientes
        SS->>DB: INSERT envios sintéticos para cubrir rango
    end
    SS->>DB: INSERT simulacion (estado=EJECUTANDO)
    SS-->>AD: 200 OK {simulacionId}

    loop Cada bloque (async)
        SS->>DB: SELECT envios WHERE simulacion_id=X AND fecha BETWEEN cursor AND cursor+Sc
        SS->>ACS: planificar(subInput, Ta*1000)
        ACS-->>SS: PlanificationSolutionOutput
        SS->>DB: INSERT bloque_resultado + asignacion_envio
        SS->>DB: UPDATE simulacion SET cursor_temporal++, bloque_actual++
        SS->>WS: SEND /topic/simulacion/{id} {progreso}
        WS-->>AD: Actualización en tiempo real
    end
```

